description: Try our easy to follow Winter Vegetable Pasta recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Pasta,Low saturated fat,Low salt,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Winter,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High fibre,Soy free,Low fat,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Winter Vegetable Pasta Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Cook pasta in a large saucepan of boiling water following packet directions. Drain and set aside.
Heat oil in the same pan over medium heat. Cook onion and garlic for 2 minutes or until softened. Add broccolini and stir for 1 minute. Add kale and cook for 2 minutes or until wilted.
Add pasta vegetable mixture and toss to combine. Add kumato and grape tomatoes. Serve with dressing and parsley.
